label goodending:
    play sound "audio/alarm.ogg" volume 0.3
    scene black with dissolve
    play music "audio/casual3.ogg" volume 0.3
    "Waking up in the morning has never felt so great, I feel full of determination, ready to ace this test whatever it is."
    stop sound
    scene fountain with llongdissolve
    "We meet the rest of our friends for a quick breakfast before gathering in the town square, where curious townspeople watch us, the students."
    "We are just as confused as you people..."
    "The Headmaster appears late as always, and explains some basic rules briefly, he's being pretty vague about this whole thing..."
    "We are each given an envelope which we are supposed to open when the test officially starts, more rules and details will be found inside."
    stop music fadeout 2.0
    "Before I know it, each student, is being teleported one by one..."
    play sound "audio/teleport.ogg"
    scene endforest with dissolve
    "I blink in front of a forest...a familiar forest, with trees many times larger than the regular trees I'm so used to."
    "In the sky I see a countdown."
    play sound "audio/timeup.ogg"
    "5"
    play sound "audio/timeup.ogg"
    "4"
    play sound "audio/timeup.ogg"
    "3"
    play sound "audio/timeup.ogg"
    "2"
    play sound "audio/timeup.ogg"
    "1"

    "The Test Begins..." with dissolve
    show wolf20
    play sound"audio/wack.ogg"
    d"{size=60}HEY!{/size}"

    d "Oops, sorry, I hope I didn't scare you."
    d "This is my first time I do this, and probably the only time, since you're probably tired of seeing my cat friend's face for so long, no matter how much you like him."
    d "I'm here to let you know this is the end of Tate's route for Chapter one."
    d "It sure was something, huh?"
    hide wolf20
    show wolf20sadsmile
    d "I'm ashamed to admit, but there were a lot of things I didn't know about this cheerful furball."
    hide wolf20sadsmile
    show wolf20ec
    d "Oh, and Congratulations!"
    d "It seems like you got {b}The Best{/b} ending of the route!"
    d "You managed to get him out of his shell, even if he would deny he ever had a shell."
    d "And that kiss was {b}stellar{/b}! So I was told."
    d "I didn't actually see it, of course."

    hide wolf20ec
    show wolf20sadsmile
    d "I was also told there could've been quite a different outcome if you betrayed the cat enough along the way."
    d "I'm glad you didn't go that path."
    hide wolf20sadsmile
    show wolf20
    d "So what did you think so far?"
    d "Our world is still early in development, but it is coming along really well!"
    d "I really hope to see you again for Chapter two."

    d "Thank you again for playing, here are some special mentions before you go."
    d "List brought to you by Chelsie, I'll just play her recording."
    ch "Yo yo, here are my friends, listen close to who my gang has to offer."
    ch "M'lady Merina, the most gracious fox, certified forever prom queen winner."
    hide wolf20
    show wolf20surprised
    ch "Aiden, the annoying tiger I like to drink with that is actually very chill when you get to know him and I definitely never got a crush on him and absolutely never fantasized about his teeth biting into my-"
    hide wolf20surprised
    show wolf20sadsmile
    ch "{i}*cough cough*{/i} I mean."
    ch "Next."
    ch "Tate, the troublemaking child we all love because he's our son, you hurt him, we bust your kneecaps."
    hide wolf20sadsmile
    show wolf20blush2
    ch "Dallan, my bestie, leader and the bestest of boys~"
    d "Oh shush~"
    hide wolf20blush2
    show wolf20
    ch "Haima, the murderous, cursed, apathetic, small leader of the Slayer's Shard, they like to be left alone, so you better do just that if you don't want some missing fingers."
    ch "Oliver, Merina's familiar."
    ch "Hehe, just kidding, but he could pass as one, he's really small and cute, I could eat him right up!"
    d "He really is."
    ch "Therium!"
    ch "..."
    d "..."
    ch "Don't know much about him..."
    ch "Coal and Rose, unstopable duo that appeared out of nowhere and took our academy by storm!"
    hide wolf20
    show wolf20simple
    ch "That little sarcastic voice inside your head."
    d "Voice?"
    ch "And of course, who could forget the most charismatic, smartest, sexiest, most beloved inventor of them all!"
    hide wolf20simple
    show wolf20
    ch "Her, the myth, the legend, she's an icon and she IS the moment:"
    ch "Chelsie, the trusty vice leader of the Defender's Shard."
    ch "Find me for cool items and trinkets, now on sale!"
    ch "Take it away, Dallan!"
    d "Right, you heard it here first."
    d "You might be wondering, after all that, when Chapter 2 is coming out?"
    d "Well, good news, only 1 path is left to be made for Chapter 1, so the answer is pretty soon!"
    d "We will get to hang out again!"
    d "Although the speed and quality will always depend on the support the game is getting."
    d "That's all for now, friends!"
    d "Have a nice day!"


    hide wolf20 with longdissolve







    jump Chapter1
